sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Cliente App
    participant APP as Web App
    participant API as ConsertaPraMim.API
    participant APPSVC as MobileClientServiceRequestService
    participant CATSVC as ServiceCategoryCatalogService
    participant DB as SQL Database

    C->>APP: Abre dashboard
    APP->>API: GET /api/mobile/client/service-requests/categories
    API->>APPSVC: GetActiveCategoriesAsync()
    APPSVC->>CATSVC: GetActiveAsync()
    CATSVC->>DB: Select ServiceCategoryDefinitions (IsActive=true)
    DB-->>CATSVC: id, name, slug, legacyCategory, icon
    CATSVC-->>APPSVC: categorias com icon
    APPSVC-->>API: MobileClientServiceRequestCategoryDto[]
    API-->>APP: 200 categorias
    APP-->>C: Renderiza categorias reais

    C->>APP: Toca em categoria X
    APP->>APP: setSelectedCategoryId(X)
    APP-->>C: Navega para Novo Pedido com categoria preselecionada
